      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Split layout: brand story (left) sells the product while the form (right) stays focused\n•  “Sign in” triggers one orchestrated transition: form fades + scales out, app shell fades + lifts in ~400ms later\n•  Live stat strip on the brand panel doubles as social proof before the user even logs in",
      "fontSize": 11.8,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
