      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783514742346,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  “Your XP this month” and “Dept. Rank” sit in the same KPI row as CO₂e and ESG Score — gamification reads as one more ESG metric, not a bolted-on app\n•  Active Challenge card shows live progress and the exact XP payout on completion\n•  Earned badges appear as a strip directly under the challenge card — no extra click needed to feel progress\n•  “View data” / “Gamification hub” links deep-link into the full Environmental list or Gamification hub respectively",
      "fontSize": 11.8,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 55,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  “Your XP this month” and “Dept. Rank” sit in the same KPI row as CO₂e and ESG Score — gamification reads as one more ESG metric, not a bolted-on app\n•  Active Challenge card shows live progress and the exact XP payout on completion\n•  Earned badges appear as a strip directly under the challenge card — no extra click needed to feel progress\n•  “View data” / “Gamification hub” links deep-link into the full Environmental list or Gamification hub respectively",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b0OV",
      "autoResize": true
    },
