      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Status pill colour-codes lifecycle (grey Draft → green Confirmed → blue Validated → red Needs review)\n•  Drawer slides in from the right over a dimmed overlay; closing it returns to the exact scroll position in the list\n•  Smart-button strip inside the drawer still links to Emission Factor, Attachments and Department Budget records\n•  Same pattern is meant to be reused for Social (CSR activities) and Governance (audits) once built out",
      "fontSize": 11.8,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 55,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Status pill colour-codes lifecycle (grey Draft → green Confirmed → blue Validated → red Needs review)\n•  Drawer slides in from the right over a dimmed overlay; closing it returns to the exact scroll position in the list\n•  Smart-button strip inside the drawer still links to Emission Factor, Attachments and Department Budget records\n•  Same pattern is meant to be reused for Social (CSR activities) and Governance (audits) once built out",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b1SV",
      "autoResize": true
    },
