    {
      "id": "inztjtg141ek7l3s",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 3370,
      "width": 1860,
      "height": 73.75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#33403a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1269026696,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 580087229,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783514742346,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Flow strip makes the XP mechanic explicit: Join → Submit proof → Admin review → XP awarded → Badge/level check\n•  Rejections loop back to “Submit proof” rather than dead-ending the employee — they always know what to do next\n•  Kanban columns mirror this same lifecycle: Active → Under Review → Completed\n•  Badges tab (not pictured at this scale) shows locked vs. earned state with the exact unlock rule per badge\n•  Leaderboard tab supports department + time-range filters (This month / All time)",
      "fontSize": 11.8,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 69.75,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Flow strip makes the XP mechanic explicit: Join → Submit proof → Admin review → XP awarded → Badge/level check\n•  Rejections loop back to “Submit proof” rather than dead-ending the employee — they always know what to do next\n•  Kanban columns mirror this same lifecycle: Active → Under Review → Completed\n•  Badges tab (not pictured at this scale) shows locked vs. earned state with the exact unlock rule per badge\n•  Leaderboard tab supports department + time-range filters (This month / All time)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b2SV",
      "autoResize": true
    },
