      "updated": 1783514742346,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  Time-range chips (This month / This quarter / FY26) scope every panel on the page at once\n•  Department comparison table shows delta vs. the previous period so movement is obvious, not just the current score\n•  Each generated report lists its format and generation date; “Export current view” creates an ad-hoc export of whatever filters are active",
      "fontSize": 11.8,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 40.25,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  Time-range chips (This month / This quarter / FY26) scope every panel on the page at once\n•  Department comparison table shows delta vs. the previous period so movement is obvious, not just the current score\n•  Each generated report lists its format and generation date; “Export current view” creates an ad-hoc export of whatever filters are active",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
