    {
      "id": "6dn0y3q4ufwsi7lx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 4118,
      "width": 1860,
      "height": 72.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#33403a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 697164766,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 2005536659,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783514742346,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "•  XP-by-difficulty table is the single source of truth an admin edits — changing it here changes payouts everywhere\n•  Bonus rules are toggleable, not hard-coded: streak bonus, department catch-up multiplier, early-bird bonus\n•  Level thresholds are named (Sprout → Guardian) so progress feels like a journey, not just a number going up\n•  Badge configuration shows live holder counts, so an admin can see if a badge is too easy (400+ holders) or too rare (10 holders) and retune it\n•  Notifications tab (not pictured at this scale) lets each lifecycle event — approved, rejected, published, unlocked — be toggled independently",
      "fontSize": 11.6,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 68.5,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "•  XP-by-difficulty table is the single source of truth an admin edits — changing it here changes payouts everywhere\n•  Bonus rules are toggleable, not hard-coded: streak bonus, department catch-up multiplier, early-bird bonus\n•  Level thresholds are named (Sprout → Guardian) so progress feels like a journey, not just a number going up\n•  Badge configuration shows live holder counts, so an admin can see if a badge is too easy (400+ holders) or too rare (10 holders) and retune it\n•  Notifications tab (not pictured at this scale) lets each lifecycle event — approved, rejected, published, unlocked — be toggled independently",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b3FV",
      "autoResize": true
    },
